reviews.text: Although ok tasty, have cockroaches inside

A cockroach crawled out from the wooden tray under my plate, but the plate was smoking hot so I assumed that it hadn’t entered the food and still ate it anyway. As I was leaving, the roach was still lingering around my seat so I told a waitress about it. But unfortunately she didn’t seem to care and did nothing about it.
Pizza was okay. The deserts were great. The Chinese food looked nice.
cheap prices but be warned portions are small

reviews.text: Good food court with low prices. Nice interior
Medium sized shopping mall and home
Many food restaurants, but the toilet is dirty
Nice unusual mall. Mainly on ground floor with some old Hong Kong style parts. Food places, bubble tea, kids playhouse, supermarket, all available here on rather small area.

It's not a bad place to visit but need to sort out the public toilets & people who works at the back of the building smoking.
If they can add baby changing room event better.
